WEBVTT

00:01.601 --> 00:03.495
It is getting cold outside.

00:04.454 --> 00:06.085
The wind is blowing.

00:07.011 --> 00:08.869
There is a nip in the air.

00:09.910 --> 00:12.466
Jamal and Isha run into the house.

00:13.514 --> 00:15.007
They get their coats.

00:16.088 --> 00:17.669
They come back outside.

00:18.694 --> 00:20.755
White flakes begin to fall.

00:21.746 --> 00:24.253
Jamal and Isha open their mouths.

00:25.245 --> 00:27.576
They catch snow on their tongues.

00:28.616 --> 00:31.148
The snow begins to fall fast.

00:32.196 --> 00:34.598
It falls faster and faster.

00:35.541 --> 00:37.171
The snow gets deep.

00:38.139 --> 00:40.297
It gets deeper and deeper.

00:41.362 --> 00:42.987
The wind blows harder.

00:44.009 --> 00:46.343
It gets colder and colder.

00:47.359 --> 00:50.157
Jamal and Isha go into the house.

00:51.174 --> 00:53.237
It feels good to be warm.

